Type-Params
===========

Created:      2013-04-10
Home page:    <https://metacpan.org/release/Type-Params>
Bug tracker:  <http://rt.cpan.org/Dist/Display.html?Queue=Type-Params>
Maintainer:   Toby Inkster <mailto:tobyink@cpan.org>

0.000_05  2013-04-26

 - (Addition) Added an 'Invocant' type constraint.
 - (Addition) Benchmarking script now also compares with Params::Check.
 - (Bugfix) Fixed validation of slurpy hash lengths.
 - (Documentation) Minor corrections.
 - (Packaging) Bigger, better test suite.

0.000_04  2013-04-26

 - (Addition) Benchmarking script now also compares with Data::Validator.
 - Include some trickery in Makefile.PL to pull in the latest dev release
   for Type-Tiny, providing better CPAN testers reports.

0.000_03  2013-04-18

 - use Exporter::TypeTiny for exporting functions.

0.000_02  2013-04-16

 - (Packaging) List dependencies.

0.000_01  2013-04-16  # Developer preview


